<h2>Folder Structure</h2>

<pre><code>Demon's Nation of Realism/
├── REPO FILES
├── Base_Pack
├── POM_Extension
└── PBR_Extension
</code></pre>

<p>
Load the Base Pack first and then choose either the POM or PBR extension. Loading both optional extensions simultaneously may cause graphical issues.
</p>

<h2>Performance Tips</h2>

<ul>
    <li>Allocate at least 8GB of RAM to Minecraft.</li>
    <li>Use OptiFine or Iris + Sodium.</li>
    <li>Install a modern graphics driver.</li>
    <li>Use SSD storage for faster loading times.</li>
    <li>Enable shaders to take full advantage of POM and PBR effects.</li>
</ul>

